high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the cabinet on the bottom right of the sink on the right.
Pick the candle up from the bottom cabinet on the far right.
Go left and turn to face the toilet that is behind.
Put the candle on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a candle on a toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the sink to the left of the toilet brush in the corner of the room.
Open the vanity cabinet door to the left of the toilet brush, pick up the light green candle from the cabinet, then close the cabinet door.
Turn left and move to the right side of the toilet next to the red rubbish bin.
Place the candle to the left of the blue spray bottle on top of the toilet cistern.
anns.task_desc: Place a candle on the toilet cistern.

high_descs: Turn left and walk ahead, veering right to the right sink.
Pick up the green candle in the bottom right cabinet.
Turn left and walk to the toilet.
Place the candle on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Place a candle on a toilet tank.
